---
import BaseLayout from '../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions / Privacy Policy"
  description="Hydration Authority terms of use and privacy policy."
>
  <article class="max-w-[820px] mx-auto py-10 prose-ha">
    <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-h1 mb-6">Terms &amp; Conditions / Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>
      Hydration Authority ("we", "our", "us") publishes editorial reviews of hydration, electrolyte, and mineral products. This site is an advertising-supported property; our editorial expenses are partially offset by commissions earned from the brands we review when readers click through to a partner site and make a purchase.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-h2 mt-8 mb-3">Editorial independence</h2>
    <p>
      Rankings and reviews reflect our own honest opinions based on our four standard criteria: taste, electrolyte and mineral content, ingredients, and sweeteners. Compensation from partner brands does not change how we score products.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-h2 mt-8 mb-3">Affiliate disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Outbound links to brand product pages may be affiliate links. If you purchase a product through one of those links, we may receive a commission at no additional cost to you.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-h2 mt-8 mb-3">Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      We do not collect personally identifiable information directly through this site. Third-party analytics tools may collect anonymous usage data (pageviews, referrer, device type) to help us improve content. By using the site you consent to this use.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-h2 mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
    <p>For editorial corrections or partnership inquiries, please contact us through the brand on the homepage.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
